16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. A. From the funds appropriated to the Office of
18 Educational Quality and Accountability in Enrolled House Bill No.
19 2766 of the 1st Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, the sum of
20 Five Hundred Thousand Dollars ($500,000.00) shall be used to provide
21 grants to school districts in this state to provide a cellphone-free
22 educational environment. Grants shall be provided on a first-come,
23 first-served basis only to school districts whose governing boards
24 of education have adopted a policy prohibiting students from using
